  "text": "MRDA [CITATION_1] contains textual transcription of multi-party real meetings, with speech acts annotations. We use a custom train/dev validation split (90/10 ratio) since this deduplication lead to a drastic size reduction of the original development set, and we subsample Statement examples so that they constitue 20% of the dataset. We also ignored the context.",
